name: Party Time HQ
overview:
Party Time HQ is your #1 source for inflatable water slides. We have the largest, biggest, tallest, water slides in Central Texas. We also have a large selection of combo units, bounce houses/moonwalks, margarita machines & concession equipment (cotton candy, sno-cone & popcorn machines), tables, chairs and tents.

Services Offered: Party Rentals, Water Slide Rentals, Combo Unit Rentals, Bounce House/Moonwalk Rentals, Slip n’ Slide Rentals, Margarita Machine Rentals, Concession Rentals, Tables & Chairs Rentals, Heating & Cooling Rentals, Generator Rentals

Hours: Monday-Friday: 8am-5pm, Saturday: 12pm-5pm

Payment Options: Cash, Visa, MasterCard, Diners, Discover, American Express
